Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我贏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去東京的事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 基本上挺順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極她能做好報導的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極？你說報瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒輪到她出場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那傢伙也夠怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和日向也聊過 不知道她到底堅強還是軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和你一起打工的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 不過結月能把報導的事完美解決
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}北海道的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別累壞自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是沒成功 你會很懊悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極挑戰…
