Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帶塊浮冰回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還不知道能不能帶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會發你些暖洋洋的照片的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在南極是不是鼻涕都會結冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想吃刨冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極真的埋著UFO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺就像要轉學了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見 搖搖布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}得暫時跟你告別了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也沒有別的送行方法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我沒想到會用這麼大排場嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨說要去南極的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家還當他笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都覺得是天方夜譚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且現在還是有人當他笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡也有三個多月沒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 只是不知道自己會是什麼心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不要太招搖比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有不少人嫌你們得意忘形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼好招搖的吧 明天就要出發啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話是這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是謠言傳得很兇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概是嫉妒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說你們為了籌錢去便利商店行竊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}經常去歌舞伎町陪男人鬼混…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是怎樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說 有人認為你們太跩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣出發真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回來後 說不定情況會更糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道說這個人就是小惠？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 日向還是第一次見到她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是和小理一起打工的三宅日向 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你剛才說的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是誰在那邊亂說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也只是聽說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕對要把犯人抓出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天就要出發了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣胡說八道 怎麼能忍氣吞聲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在把事情鬧大也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們一直都對風言風語不理不睬的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}繼續無視就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這可不一樣 這些都是假話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們哪有去新宿跟男人鬼混
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事實就是去過新宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才沒有鬼混
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能證明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠 你怎麼看？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你問我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每個人都有惡毒的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要以惡報惡 挺起胸膛做人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}名言？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且現在在這裡的也不止你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有能傾吐不滿的對象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這個味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來下班途中喝一杯 就是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好咧 再來一罐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天發薪水 我請你們喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我還是很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是記仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是錯肯定在傳謠言的人身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}憑什麼我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂我懂 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想盡情大吼發洩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就吼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在寺廟後大吼大叫不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就去卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有一個小時 應該沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還沒去過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼大家敢做那麼丟人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大聲吼出來就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就當是餞別會啦 餞別會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠也要去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氣氛嗨起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小淵澤報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就高橋惠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的好友小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氣氛嗨起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小淵澤報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小淵澤報瀨 小淵澤報瀨 小淵澤報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.94,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康布丁體W7\bord0\fs65\frz274\frx338\fry4\1c&H6370CB&\be2\move(1150,22,1144,402,0,658)}報{\1c&H64D8BD&}瀨{\1c&HCED9AA&}瘋{\1c&H3DDFEB&}了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:50.49,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康布丁體W7\bord0\fs65\frz274\frx338\fry4\1c&H6370CB&\be2\move(1144,402,1142,62,0,2566)}報{\1c&H64D8BD&}瀨{\1c&HCED9AA&}瘋{\1c&H3DDFEB&}了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還好沒跟她們一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 最棒的一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒想到出發前一天還能來這麼一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想 自從決定去南極之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就沒什麼機會和你一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然小惠你好像不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那種事…算了 其實我也是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是我心裡很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直都在想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想去遙遠的地方啦 不想待在這裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}討厭自己之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我為什麼會有這些想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概是因為小惠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我總是慢吞吞的 一直要小惠照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老是黏著你問東問西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有這回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我討厭這點 所以一直想改變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想黏在你身邊 不想當你口中的廢柴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少想成為你遊戲的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是怎樣 好豐盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼晚才回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就當送行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可不止那些喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來啦 雞蛋天國
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.84,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs20\1c&HB0A993&\frz4.023\pos(548,32)}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.84,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs20\1c&H6A6B6A&\frz3.948\be1\pos(484,174)}來吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走了 我走了 我走了 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:16.84,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\fnGen Jyuu Gothic Heavy\fs80\xshad-5\1c&H4856A6&\3c&H354060&\4c&H3D4664&\frz2.458\frx348\fry0\pos(512,192)}在房間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.81,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fnGen Jyuu Gothic Heavy\fs80\xshad-5\1c&HAD8769&\3c&H354060&\4c&H756048&\frz2.458\pos(512,192)\frx334\fry358}出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要出發了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要在東京吃早餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不叫醒我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會加油不讓你擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 出發日早上來見你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我來和你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說和你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說你 還沒注意到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你和南極去新宿的事 為什麼傳開來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你和別人說過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你最初遇上南極時 為什麼高年級的知道她有100萬？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你還沒開口 你媽就知道你要去南極了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除了我還能是誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還以為你很快會發現 然後大發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是真這麼以為的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是時間上的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是你跟南極她們都像個笨蛋一樣沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:16.76,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}そっと「会いたい」聞いた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:25.18,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}空に溶けて消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:42.78,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今も胸の奥　静かに揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:50.54,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}白く輝く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:58.88,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}残した足跡も消えて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:06.97,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}果てないと思ってた時が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:15.36,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}終わりを告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:25.20,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}だからずっと忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:34.62,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}言葉より大切な思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:43.93,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}きっと繋いでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:55.81,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いつの日か　また旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:07.37,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}だからずっと忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:17.00,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}一緒にいた　かけがえのない時が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:26.22,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}きっと繋いでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:37.94,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いつまでも　いつまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:43.19,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}またね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:16.76,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}聽見一聲輕輕的「想見你」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:25.18,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}聲音漸漸消失在了空中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:42.78,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我的心底依然在暗自動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:50.54,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}雪白閃耀的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:58.88,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我們踩下的足跡 漸漸褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:06.97,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}原以為這些時光 永無止境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:15.36,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}卻突然畫上了句號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:25.20,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}所以這份心情 我不會忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:34.62,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}它比任何語言 都要寶貴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:43.93,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}總有一天 會再度牽起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:55.81,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}帶著我們 又一次踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:07.37,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}所以這些時光 我不會忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:17.00,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}你我一道 度過的珍貴點滴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:26.22,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}想必它們 會永遠牽起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:37.94,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}直到永遠 直到永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:43.19,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一開始跟我說要去南極的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就在想為什麼我會這麼生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理以前不管做什麼都會先找我商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}騙人的吧 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉讓你留下不好的回憶 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨天聽你一說 我才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直黏著人的不是你 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你會依靠我 會找我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就會裝出一副 拿你沒轍只好幫幫你的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總是什麼都明白似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為不這麼做 我就一無所有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為自己一無所有 所以想讓你也一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}廢柴的不是你 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必須走出這個小世界的 是我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說什麼傻話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我終於打算向 沒有你的世界前進了啊
